c: 13
v: 11
t: "Yalli malaykay seehadayti dacayrih sittal ciggilta le, is Yallih amrih umaane celli haytaamak foocaa kee derrek kaa dacrissa;diggah Yalli seehadah yecee niqmat keenik ma seelabaay keenik makorsa, usun sinni nafsih Yalli ken kah amrise meqe taama cabbaay uma taamah abittô fanah gacca iyyaanam fanah, Yalli sinaamal digaalah bala oobisam faxek, toysa tet keenik gacissaah waasam matan, usun Yallak kalah awlaytuy keenil obta bala keenik waasaah keenik cata malon"